- send_strategy_notification() - WebSocket notifications âœ…

**Task Features:** âœ…
- Retry logic with exponential backoff âœ…
- Error handling and logging âœ…
- Strategy status updates âœ…
- Performance tracking âœ…
- Celery Beat scheduling âœ…

